HEADWORD: Ischiocapsular
<hw>Is`chi*o*cap"su*lar</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr> <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Ischium</ets> + <ets>capsular</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to the ischium and the capsule
